name: AlbanianIdNumberTest
description: Unit tests for the AlbanianIdNumber class, focusing on various methods related to generating and validating Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: valid
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a valid Albanian ID number and verifies its length.

test_cases.name: invalid
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an invalid Albanian ID number, verifies its length, and checks a specific substring for validity.

test_cases.name: yy
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of year values to a specific format used in Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: mm
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of month values to a specific format based on gender in Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: dd
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of day values to a specific format used in Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: checksum
test_cases.description: Tests the calculation of the checksum character for a given Albanian ID number.

test_cases.name: checksumOfFirstChar
test_cases.description: Tests the calculation of the checksum value for the first character of an Albanian ID number.
